  /en/alerts.html added with hreflang pairs to JP; reciprocal EN hreflang
  also added on the JP /products.html, /widget.html, /alerts.html entries.
  /en/widget/demo.html and /en/dashboard.html stay out of the sitemap
  (demo.html and dashboard.html are noindex).
  Updated 2026-04-26: EN /en/line.html, /en/advisors.html, and
  /en/facts.html added with hreflang pairs to JP; reciprocal EN hreflang
  also added on the JP /line.html, /advisors.html, /facts.html entries.
  Updated 2026-04-26: EN /en/confidence.html added with hreflang
  pair to JP; reciprocal EN hreflang added on JP /confidence.html.
  /alerts-unsubscribe.html and /en/alerts-unsubscribe.html stay out of the
  sitemap (both noindex,nofollow — confirmation surface only).
