  /en/prompts.html added with hreflang pairs to JP; reciprocal EN hreflang
  also added on the JP /partners.html and /prompts.html entries.
  Updated 2026-04-26: /compare.html and /en/compare.html added
  with hreflang pairs (neutral 6-service / 13-axis comparison page).
  /sources.html and /en/sources.html already present; /facts.html JP/EN
  also already present. /humans.txt already present.
  Updated 2026-04-29: /status/ live status page added (trust
  signal for prospect evaluation). Distinct from /status.html which is the
  static fallback served on DNS flip during incidents — that one stays
  noindex. The new /status/index.html polls /v1/am/health/deep + PyPI from
  the browser; index,follow so it can rank for "AutonoMath status" queries.

  Excluded by design:
    - /en/tokushoho.html (noindex — JP-only legal surface with EN pointer)
